# lines are elided -- stdout from the `header:` line is the gate record.
# Gates: G1 maker-price-fill | G2 price-time | G5 no-float | G6 self-trade |
#        AS-7 fill-key-freeze (2000 seeded crossing runs) | AS-2 pure-grep.
# Spec: docs/exchange/trd.2.1.specs.md ("Acceptance gates").
